    "31 propose Point-Set Anchors, which uses a set of anchor points for HPE.",
    "The method represents human pose as a set of point-set anchors and uses a neural network to detect and regress these anchors, thereby obtaining the human pose.",
    "However, this method relies on the selection of initial anchors, and different initial anchors may have an impact on the results.",
